original_title: Rick Lee James: Basement Psalms Live
overview: Singer, songwriter, and author (Out of the Depths) Rick lee James takes you on a musical journey through the book of Psalms with 10 original songs and stories. Filmed lived at the Clifton Opera House in Clifton Ohio with a special guest appearance by songwriter and worship leader Brannon Hancock.
title: Rick Lee James: Basement Psalms Live
